  "text": "In the third approach we estimate a query model that differentiate the language use of the query patent from the collection model. As suggested by Hiemstra et al. [CITATION_1] , we estimate the topic of the query patent following the parsimonious language modeling, by concentrating the probability mass on terms that are indicator of the topic of the query patent and are dissimilar from the collection model. We use EM-algorithm for estimating the query model of different fields of a patent document. Parsimonious Query Model P QM f is estimated according to the following iterative algorithm: E-step:",
